    "detail": "I had a morning flight home to USA and wanted to be closer to the airport the night before flying home. Spent one night at this hotel which was very reasonably priced compared to what you have to pay in central London. You can take the TFL rain or Heathrow Express to airport (we did Tfl rail which is cheaper but takes slightly longer). From the airport you can take a free city bus (double decker which my daughter loved) which drops you off right across from the hotel. The next morning we took the free bus again from the hotel to the terminal. No need to pay for the Hoppa bus. ",
